<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Redemption Songs 92, Key G</author>
<hymn_number>305</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Samari lam khawm lui ah, Thu kipahum gen a hi;
 Thagau dangchaknu kawmah, Sawt lamin;
 Vak mulo sawt tak um, Chun vakna lopi a mui;
 Lui chu hawn a hihtak ziekin, Sawt lamin.

[V2]
 Lui a um hi, hawn a hi tai, Sawt lamin, Sawt lamin;
 Zie lui luong chu namtin damna ding ahi,
 Sawt apat zie lui achun Thiemgaute leh mithieng te'n;
 Damna lui luong chu a na muu, Sawt lamin.

[V3]
 2. Galhat miphakpa kawmah, Saltang numei naupang chun,
 Thusim mawltak chu a gen, Sawt lamin;
 A ki diehna ding lui mai chun hihdam theihna a nei;
 Ginnan a damtai tui achun, Sawt lamin.

[V4]
 3. Mipi laka numei khat, pau lo thip kei a um in;
 Khunin, a puon mawng a tham, Sawt lamin,
 A thildeih chu a mu tai, A thagau hukdamna tawh,
 Luikhuk hawnsa a um achun, Sawt lamin.

[V5]
 4. Mitilgehpa lehkha sim Philip in a hilhchiena,
 Lui achun a Baptis tai, Sawt lamin;
 Sunggila Pathien nasep pawlama tiemtehna din,
 Lui achun bawlin a um tai, Sawt lamin.</lyrics>
<title>The Old Fountain</title>
</song>